card.name: Acolyte of the Sun
card.flavor_text: The light of faith becomes the source of life.

card.name: Atom Seikhart
card.flavor_text: A hundred years prior, Kaguya's influence transformed many rabbits into wererabbits. The only true rabbit remaining is he.

card.name: Atom Seikhart, the Shimmering Rabbit
card.flavor_text: "Is it finally time? It would seem my services are needed once again."

card.name: Bethor, the Angel of Treasure
card.flavor_text: As long as her wings still fly, nobody, not even Atom, dared near the treasure.

card.name: Bewilder
card.flavor_text: Hallucinations produce momentary confusion.

card.name: Brunhild
card.flavor_text: The leader of the Valkyries and the voice of Odin.

card.name: Brunhild, Caller of Spirits
card.flavor_text: Souls chosen by Brunhild return to the battlefield as heroes.

card.name: Brunhild's Wrath
card.flavor_text: "Don't expect those girls to show you any goodwill. Their faith is an ideology far removed from the likes of compassion." -Atom Seikhart

card.name: Dispel
card.flavor_text: Everything that does not adhere to their faith is a target for destruction.

card.name: Einherjar's Summons
card.flavor_text: Brunhild ushers in the souls of the fallen heroes.

card.name: Eir, Valkyrie of Mercy
card.flavor_text: The warrior who fell in battle is given another chance at glory.

card.name: Karmic Reversal
card.flavor_text: "Carelessness bares face just as one thinks they've won. That is to say, the best time to turn the tables is at the very last moment of the battle." -Atom Seikhart

card.name: Mini Meteor
card.flavor_text: "What's wrong? This much isn't anything to be afraid of." -Atom Seikhart

card.name: Odin's Judgment
card.flavor_text: "Lord, grant your benevolent judgement upon these knaves." -Brunhild

card.name: Phaleg, the Angel of War
card.flavor_text: War is determined by who makes the first strike.

card.name: Phul, the Administrator of the Moon
card.flavor_text: The angels dispatched by Zeus had protected Lunar Heaven this whole time.

card.name: Ring of Legend
card.flavor_text: The real deal is more than simple decoration.

card.name: Sigrun, Valkyrie of Victory
card.flavor_text: "Victory shall be attained by our hands!"

card.name: Sorceress of the Moon
card.flavor_text: The rabbits of Lunar Heaven have learned to utilize the vestiges of magic left from activated runes, amplifying their own power.

card.name: The Valkyrie's Chosen
card.flavor_text: Within the soldier lies an unwavering spirit.

card.name: Turn Tail
card.flavor_text: First lesson of Lunar Heaven Academy: How to Run Away.

card.name: Warrior of the Sun
card.flavor_text: The sun grants upon the warrior the courage needed to fight.

card.name: Wererabbit Warrior
card.flavor_text: The rabbit's ears heard the sounds of a distant battle. Following them, he leapt into the fray.

card.name: Zeus' Grand Lightning
card.flavor_text: "Don't resent me for this!" -Atom Seikhart

card.name: Chu-Ko-Nu Soldier
card.flavor_text: The last bolt is oneself.

card.name: Concealed Khopesh
card.flavor_text: "This will be the last thing you see!" -Isis

card.name: Dragon Dance
card.flavor_text: The dance of the dragon inspires the soldiers.

card.name: Dragon of Kunlun
card.flavor_text: A dragon's warm reception begins with fire.

card.name: Dragon's Flight
card.flavor_text: Whenever a dragon begins flight, the vast lands of Kunlun start to sway.

card.name: Explosion
card.flavor_text: Only silence followed the explosion.

card.name: Flame Enchant
card.flavor_text: The divine power sleeping within Isis grants her the ability to enchant objects with fire.

card.name: Flame Soldier Formation
card.flavor_text: "While a frontal attack may be good, we should also incorporate some other strategies... Hey, Pang Tong! You listening?" -Zhuge Liang

card.name: Fu Xi
card.flavor_text: The ruler of Kunlun is always prepared for war.

card.name: Fu Xi, King of Kunlun
card.flavor_text: "Let me show you what it means to be king."

card.name: Giant Sandstorm
card.flavor_text: The sand loves Sandora, but cares little for anything else.

card.name: Isis
card.flavor_text: The gods who birthed Sandora from nothing distributed their own power to a few humans, those of which would later rule as Ascendants.

card.name: Isis, the Hundred Weapon Master
card.flavor_text: Her ultimate attack resembles petals scattering in the wind, earning her the title the "Flower of the Desert".

card.name: Magician of Molding
card.flavor_text: Using a little imagination, sand can be molded into anything.

card.name: Pang Tong
card.flavor_text: Known affectionately as the "Young Phoenix", this young man serves as Fu Xi's advisor.

card.name: Poison Stinger
card.flavor_text: The actual damage the stinger does is low, but it contains a poison that lowers the target's resistances considerably.

card.name: Reckless Flame Soldier
card.flavor_text: There is no greater beauty than the burning of life.

card.name: Sand Dragon
card.flavor_text: The needed materials are all around Sandora.

card.name: Sandora Blacksmith
card.flavor_text: When crafting arms, the slightest mistake can be the difference between life and death.

card.name: Sandworm
card.flavor_text: A swift and intelligent hunter of the desert.

card.name: Set, the Commander of Destruction
card.flavor_text: "Let's see which breaks first, your mind or your body."

card.name: Soldier Ambush
card.flavor_text: "This is where you'll meet your end!...I always wanted to try saying that!" -Pang Tong

card.name: Tiger of Kunlun
card.flavor_text: "It's not that the tiger is strong, you're all just too weak." -Fu Xi

card.name: Whirlwind Conflagration
card.flavor_text: "Shed as much blood as you like. In the end, the sand will wash it all away." -Isis

card.name: Anti-Matter Cannon, Excalibur
card.flavor_text: Sky Round's ultimate weapon.

card.name: Arthur
card.flavor_text: Within the castle in the sky lies Arthur and his knights of steel.

card.name: Arthur, King of Machines
card.flavor_text: The knights, created by Deus Ex Machina, continue to carry out their duties in this world.

card.name: Caliburn, the Sword of Judgment
card.flavor_text: "I'll let you choose who survives." -Arthur

card.name: Charm
card.flavor_text: "Come to me." -Loki

card.name: Checkmate
card.flavor_text: This is the end.

card.name: Consume
card.flavor_text: "Mmm, bon app?tit." -Loki

card.name: Donut Drone
card.flavor_text: Excellent for reconnaissance, as well as for scrap parts.

card.name: Gawain, the Swift Knight
card.flavor_text: Those who are granted knightship undergo alterations in order to better serve their lord.

card.name: Gretel of Misty Woods
card.flavor_text: Loki took interest in the children's story of another world, one where fairy tales flourished. It wouldn't hurt to have another world to play in.

card.name: Hansel of Misty Woods
card.flavor_text: "Welcome, children." -Loki

card.name: Loki
card.flavor_text: "Now then, let's get this show on the road."

card.name: Loki, the Witch of Chaos
card.flavor_text: "The power of the gods... Hehehe... I wonder, will they manage to master it?"

card.name: Loki's Watchdog, Fenrir
card.flavor_text: "Grab me some too, Fenrir!" -Loki

card.name: Maintenance
card.flavor_text: For these knights, oil is the same as blood.

card.name: Mechanical Bishop
card.flavor_text: Just like how humans save one another, machines do the same.

card.name: Mechanical Soldier
card.flavor_text: The fact that they only move as instructed has its ups and downs.

card.name: Monstrosify
card.flavor_text: The weaker the person, the more fearsome the monster they hold in their heart.

card.name: Overflowing Knowledge
card.flavor_text: Loki sealed away her infinite pool of knowledge, releasing it piece by piece whenever she felt the need.

card.name: Perceval, the Shining Knight
card.flavor_text: "Stand back. I'll handle the rest."

card.name: Petrification
card.flavor_text: "I'm going to go take a nap, quiet down for me." -Loki

card.name: Reconnaissance
card.flavor_text: The Knights of Sky Round are always watching over the world.

card.name: Scarecrow Guide
card.flavor_text: This harrowing scarecrow leads unwise travelers deep into the forest, never to be seen again.

card.name: Witch's House
card.flavor_text: Hansel and Gretel came upon a strange cottage in the woods.

card.name: Chamimi
card.flavor_text: "If a trespasser comes, let me know right away mi-!"

card.name: Chamimi, Guardian of the Sacred Bow
card.flavor_text: "You'll regret stepping foot onto our sacred grounds mi-!"

card.name: Chiyome, the Captivating Kunoichi
card.flavor_text: Her seduction techniques are the best in the world. It's a shame they only work on cats.

card.name: Elephant Rush!!
card.flavor_text: "Stomp them underfoot mi-!" -Chamimi

card.name: Fairy of the Lost Isles
card.flavor_text: The Mimi tribe consider the fairies close friends. The fairies, on the other hand, find the constant "Mi-! Mi-!" to be annoying and would rather they didn't.

card.name: Forest Meditation
card.flavor_text: The god of the forest grants a mysterious power to those who pray.

card.name: Fuhma Shuriken
card.flavor_text: "My shurikens do quite a number. A well placed one can incapacitate any foe." -Hanzo

card.name: Grand Mallet Warrior
card.flavor_text: A giant mallet has merit as both a weapon and a tenderizer.

card.name: Hanzo
card.flavor_text: The Kouga are a peculiar group of cats and youkai. Why is a cat in charge? Only god knows.

card.name: Hanzo, Chief of the Kouga
card.flavor_text: "Would you kindly surrender to me? No? Very well then, while it is not my nature to kill, I see it cannot be helped!"

card.name: Huge Toad
card.flavor_text: While it may be Jiraiya's ride, its strength is nothing to scoff at.

card.name: Jiraiya, the Toad User
card.flavor_text: Even if Jiraiya is defeated, the toads continue the fight. Such a strong drive is one of their appeals.

card.name: Mu, the Hero of the Greatshield
card.flavor_text: While he may be small in stature, his courage is anything but.

card.name: Pygmy Hippo
card.flavor_text: Lost Isles' unique ecosystem comes with a trove of rare animals.

card.name: Raft Downstream
card.flavor_text: The river is the most dangerous place in Lost Isles. You never know when a Mimi tribesman will come flowing down.

card.name: Rapid Fire Mi-!!
card.flavor_text: "Kill 'em all mi-!"

card.name: Sanctuary Elephant
card.flavor_text: Raising such robust elephants also carries a downside. Every now and then an elephant gets too excited, crushing a Mimi tribe dwelling. A sad "Mi..." can be heard when this happens.

card.name: Sealing Scroll
card.flavor_text: This divine power sealing technique is a secret art passed down only to the chiefs of the Kouga clan.

card.name: Shadow Step
card.flavor_text: If he felt like it, he could even outrun his shadow.

card.name: Snipe Away Mi-!!
card.flavor_text: "It's too late to beg for your lives mi-!"

card.name: Soot Sprite
card.flavor_text: The Kouga utilized these small youkai as messengers.

card.name: Spirited Away
card.flavor_text: "Not even I know where they go." -Hanzo

card.name: The Hundred Eyed One
card.flavor_text: Despite all the eyes, its eyesight is surprisingly poor.

card.name: Whirlwind Technique
card.flavor_text: A technique to protect from projectiles.

card.name: Armaros, the Fallen Angel of Nullification
card.flavor_text: "One would do best not to carelessly approach. Of course, I'll do the same." -Atom Seikhart

card.name: Black Rosario
card.flavor_text: "This grave-post shall be my last gift to you." -Lucifer

card.name: Cycle of Death
card.flavor_text: We are born unequal, yet die all the same.

card.name: Demon Division
card.flavor_text: The demons will always hear out your wish. Whether or not they grant it is up to their whims.

card.name: Fanatic of Grief
card.flavor_text: Faith is always accompanied by madness.

card.name: Fleurety
card.flavor_text: The rains of Rainruins bore holes into one's spirit.

card.name: Immortal Commander
card.flavor_text: Vampires reign as the strongest of the undead.

card.name: Jet-Black Wings
card.flavor_text: The jet-black wings dance about in the sky, all who touch it have their lives taken away.

card.name: Lich
card.flavor_text: Those with noble spirit in life gain immense dark power when turned undead.

card.name: Lich, the Saint of Death
card.flavor_text: Death itself speaks highly of the Lich.

card.name: Lower Fallen Angel
card.flavor_text: An army of grief blankets the sky, an ill omen for those below.

card.name: Lucifer
card.flavor_text: The leader of the fallen angels chose the depths of these ancient ruins as his home.

card.name: Lucifer, Fallen Angel of Sorrow
card.flavor_text: As his tears fell, so did the last of his love.

card.name: Patchwork Frankenstein
card.flavor_text: Each time it moves, another piece comes falling off.

card.name: Putrefy
card.flavor_text: The best way to prolong the pain.

card.name: Scythe of the Reaper
card.flavor_text: The weak may try to run, but death always follows.

card.name: Shemhaza, the Fallen Angel of Sadism
card.flavor_text: "Now, offer your body and soul to me."

card.name: Skeleton Horde
card.flavor_text: Even if you crush their bones, they'll reassemble and stand again.

card.name: Specter Rush
card.flavor_text: Death eventually comes to claim the souls of the living.

card.name: Sword of Lament
card.flavor_text: A blade of cruelty.

card.name: Tears of the Fallen
card.flavor_text: The tears of the heartbroken rain down on this land.

card.name: Undeath
card.flavor_text: The chasm of the abyss loves the dead, almost as much as it loves to bring them back.

card.name: Vlad, the Insatiable
card.flavor_text: A vampire's thirst never ceases.

card.name: Wanderer of the Abyss
card.flavor_text: As long as you are in the abyss, you can never run out of the dead.
